# ── firewall belt-and-braces ─────────────────────────────────────────
# The Enka _repo is a public github (auralumi33/enkakanopi-world) and
# must never track anything from adjacent ventures or private doctrine.
# The workspace one level up carries P0–P10 material; these patterns
# make it impossible for a stray copy/symlink into _repo to be staged.
# See enka-airlock-firewall SKILL.md for the crossing rules (LESSONS.md
# via tools/lesson-gate.sh is the ONLY sanctioned inbound path).

# priority-folder prefixes from the venture workspace
P0-*
P1-*
P2-*
P3-*
P4-*
P5-*
P6-*
P7-*
P8-*
P9-*
P10-*

# private doctrine + succession that lives one level up
SUCCESSION.md
HANDOFF-*.md
HANDOFF-*
STUDIO-CHARTER.md
ENKA-VOICE-*.md
CALIBRATION-DOCTRINE.md
MULTI-AGENT-FOUNDATION.md
CHARTER-*.md
implementation-notes.md

# P2 personal-workspace filename patterns
HERMIT-*
HERMIT-*.md

# per-venture memory dirs that live outside _repo
_memory/
../SUCCESSION.md
